    "Fashion industry also takes advantage of GenAI by using AI-models for their fashion campaigns and presenting the clothes virtually (Demopoulus, 2023) (through images or videos).",
    "Having an AI-model saves costs with the photographer, make-up artist, hair artist etc.",
    "Fashion shows might also be organised in the metaverse (Peter, 2023), where AI models walk on the runway, wearing the digital twins (Fallmann, 2022) of the branded clothes.",
